{"tid":469802,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人瞓咗 有冇人未瞓","createTime":"2017-11-15T16:29:53.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-15T23:26:33.000Z","uid":107494,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"add2b3dfe6fc6fd6cda98526bf14edbf1c4f19d9","tid":469802,"uid":107494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T16:29:53.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我就係需要係依個鐘數都仲未瞓既年輕人</span><br />\n<br />\n是咁的，小弟近排想搞個網絡電台<br />\n<br />\n事原小弟對電台有一份獨特嘅情懷  可能之前自己又無份拍拖 唯有上電臺聽聽眾叫春 睇吓佢哋拍拖有幾慘 自我安慰下 諗返起原來電台都係一種娛樂 留不住的感覺<br />\n<br />\n細個覺得如果返工又有水吹又可以開拓眼界 不失爲一份筍工  不過......依個世界邊有咁易<br />\n<br />\n科技一日千里 竟然誕生咗一個全新既行業'直播'  依但平台真係令好多人受惠 包括我<br />\n但係直播界有好多唔同類型 '男打機 女賣肉' 係直播界既家常便飯 不禁令人覺得直播冇離正經 <br />\n<br />\n係半年前既一個晚上 我忽發奇想如果係直播到做電台 又會唔會可行呢？<br />\n<br />\n宜家人人都做DJ 唔通人人想做DJ咩<br />\n<br />\n咁我就想搞風煙電台 主要係想懷念已逝去既1872遊花園 就算幾忙都好 夢想始終都係放唔低 一個係夜晚同聽眾傾心事既DJ<br />\n<br />\n  雖然我要翻工 直播既時間可能唔多 不過幾攰都好 我都想盡量實現呢個夢想 我會花光所有心機同時間落去實行 但係直播方面都可能一星期只有一兩日 我希望有興趣既人都可以加入 一完電台夢  <br />\n<br />\n 我地風煙既方式會係經Skype 大家可以過黎分享趣事 同時希望緬懷遊花園既人可以懷緬 唔知道既人都可以過黎感受下以前既氣氛 <br />\n<br />\n你地只要係直播時留低Skype 我就會打電話比您地 <br />\n<br />\n每次討論既主題類型都唔同 仲會有好多唔同既活動環節 如果各位有興趣 不妨聯絡我大家一齊商討或者加入FB <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/%E7%8D%A8%E8%98%8B%E6%9E%9CLApple-1904427313216701/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F%25E7%258D%25A8%25E8%2598%258B%25E6%259E%259CLApple-1904427313216701%2F&d=mVBMGW%2F4qRvfiGhMNBV%2FNUbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=9cefdf89\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/%E7%8D%A8%E8%98%8B%E6%9E%9CLApple-1904427313216701/</a><br />\n<br />\n希望各位捧下場 過黎食住花生 談笑風生<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCksXp1cIh0Zx06Ups7KydIA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fchannel%2FUCksXp1cIh0Zx06Ups7KydIA&d=mVBMGW%2F4qRvfiGhMNBV%2FNUbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=0a7e59ef\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCksXp1cIh0Zx06Ups7KydIA</a><br />\n<br />\n直播時間（01:00-02:00）"},{"pid":"eac23635c9388d2aae5b620f0d21c2eae7ead5f4","tid":469802,"uid":107494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T16:30:18.000Z","msg":"1872 遊花園（私服）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/469419/page/2?ref=ios\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/469419/page/2?ref=ios</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"cf948ff288547c584c58221066d31330faf2fad0","tid":469802,"uid":107494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T16:30:33.000Z","msg":"直播台太少人了"},{"pid":"4cdbdf265af0e9db605ad74606c04da1af9e18d3","tid":469802,"uid":107494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T16:31:41.000Z","msg":"有咩都可以問 晏少少答大家"},{"pid":"aebcee1f14399fc3fffdf232235675239b5d2796","tid":469802,"uid":4852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T17:00:02.000Z","msg":"支持樓主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8b65f5e14f2c515ec5c1dfcd23511e181a7622f","tid":469802,"uid":82436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T17:04:31.000Z","msg":"開左台會聽，支持"},{"pid":"b5ef26e1ce042182682da4a7655a44cba6eeabd1","tid":469802,"uid":107494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T17:22:45.000Z","msg":"多謝支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n加Youtube同Facebook測試一定會抽你地上黎傾計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"523ddf1b744f56f56bb401f516bf261ae4f03b3c","tid":469802,"uid":158349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T17:23:43.000Z","msg":"樓主寫字都咁掂<br />\n口才一定了得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n開台第一個去聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cd6db5dc914cea0f96e1de9b4d03934e596e8c7","tid":469802,"uid":107494,